title: So this song sounds like it's about Morgana and Kayle

embed.description: Love The Way You Lie (Demo from Skylar Grey) She's currently in the early stages recording her album with Alex Da Kid.

body:
I have been listening to this song on repeat because I'm incredibly depressed and all I can think of is how it reminds me of the Kayle\Morgana lore. 

Random thoughts.
